          <p className="text-xl text-gray-400 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            A premier collective of services, entertainment, and artisanal products curated for the modern visionary.
          </p>
          <div className="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
             <div className="flex items-center gap-2 glass-card px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-futuristic uppercase tracking-widest text-red-500 border-red-500/30">
